le-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\"></span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"非遗跑酷\" author=\"字节跳动技术团队\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E9%9D%9E%E9%81%97%E8%B7%91%E9%85%B7&amp;play_length=2%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" isaac2=\"1\" low_size=\"255.38\" source_size=\"255.4\" high_size=\"534.42\" play_length=\"137000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzI1MzYzMjE0MV8yMjQ3NTE0Njg3\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/5EcwYhllQOgs2G4tLib98RjWyDaGEOd8nyjkZZZQIH52V4bFnqX0mXE637zbUyB9SzlV180wt9ZvkkT7xxsaumA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过以上的播客，可以听出，相比普通的 AI 播客，扣子空间全新升级的播客有以下特点：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">更生动</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">不同于以往 AI 生成的生硬语音，扣子空间模拟真人专业播客的口语习惯，双人对谈，交叉附和，“捧哏”与“逗哏”配合默契，听觉效果高度拟人。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">更自然</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子空间全面升级播客音色，不再是冰冷的机械音，而在拟人音色中加入丰富的情感波动和丝滑的语气转换，仿佛挚友对谈，声音更有温度。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 